<p><a name="Trailer" id="Trailer"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Superman_II:_The_Richard_Donner_Cut&amp;action=edit&amp;section=15" title="Edit section: Trailer">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Trailer</span></h2>
<p>On <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="2006-09-20"><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="09-20"><a href="/wiki/September_20" title="September 20">September 20</a></span>, <a href="/wiki/2006" title="2006">2006</a></span>, <i>Warner Bros.</i> released the official trailer for the Christopher Reeve Superman Collection DVD box set. (Includes footage of <i>Superman II: The Richard Donner Cut</i>.) <a href="http://www.totaleclips.com/player/Bounce.aspx?eclipid=e29065&amp;bitrateid=214&amp;vendorid=235" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.totaleclips.com/player/Bounce.aspx?eclipid=e29065&amp;bitrateid=214&amp;vendorid=235" rel="nofollow">[2]</a></p>
